Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.92,0:00:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,蛭魅妳依舊這麼動人 完美無瑕...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.06,0:00:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 埃斯特爾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.00,0:00:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.44,0:00:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,過得好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.54,0:00:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼啦 埃斯特爾?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.22,0:00:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,無精打采的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.02,0:00:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.86,0:00:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,誒? 人家怎麼會只穿著內褲啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.16,0:00:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,蛭魅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.86,0:00:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不對 她不是蛭魅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.29,0:00:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是檮杌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.06,0:00:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,蛭魅已經死了...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.02,0:01:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,唉 先用這個將就點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.16,0:01:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,討厭啦 超丟臉的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.88,0:01:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 埃斯特爾那身裝扮是怎樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.60,0:01:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,難道是Cosplay的嗜好覺醒了喵?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.28,0:01:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.08,0:01:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,埃斯特爾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.44,0:01:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那是...怎麼回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.32,0:01:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.28,0:01:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,唷 蛭魅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.68,0:01:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,安裝成功了唷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.94,0:01:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼一來 蛭魅就...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.18,0:01:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.88,0:01:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼 要刺傷哥哥?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.02,0:01:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,埃斯特爾!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.72,0:02:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,啟動了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.46,0:02:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼一來妳就真的成為LEVEL 6囉 蛭魅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.72,0:02:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那什麼?
